HEADWORD: Promptness
<hw>Prompt"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Promptitude; readiness; quickness of decision or
action.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Cheerful willingness; alacrity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prompt-note</ent>⟦br⟧
